Award-winning music producer, Adesanya Doyinsola aka D’Tunes or deetunesagain has compared Nigerian artistes to politicians. The CEO Difference Entertainment, in an Instagram post, argued they share similarities in so many ways. “In so many ways, Nigerian artistes are very similar to Nigerian politicians,” the arts and fashion enthusiast wrote.   It’s time 2Baba gets vasectomy – Shade Ladipo     Reactions as Julius Agwu announces return of comedy show     Osinachi’s husband should be imprisoned – Uche…   Empahsising his assertion, D’Tunes stated one common similarity with artistes and politicians is ‘selfishness’ adding it’s an inherent trait among them. “Artistes …Politicians…u…me…all have 1 thing in common….. (Selfishness is the Natural state of our human mind)….#Factz,” he added.